f
C^2
\mathbb{R}^n
N
\mathbb{R}^n
u:=N\star f
\Delta u=f
C>0
x\in\mathbb{R}^n
\lVert x\rVert\geq C
 \lvert u(x)\rvert=\begin{cases}C\lVert x\rVert^{n-2}, &\mbox{ if }n\geq 3\\C\ln\lVert x\rVert, &\mbox{ if }n=2\end{cases} 
n=2
T:=\mbox{supp}(f)
\exists M\geq 0: \lVert\tau\rVert\leq M~\forall~\tau\in T
\lVert x\rVert\geq\max\left\{2,M\right\}
 \lvert u(x)\rvert\leq\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_T\lvert\ln\lVert x-\tau\rVert f(\tau)\rvert\, d\tau\\\leq\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_T\lvert\ln(2\lVert x\rVert)f(\tau)\rvert\, d\tau\\\leq\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_T\lvert 2\ln\lVert x\rVert f(\tau)\rvert\, d\tau\\=\underbrace{\frac{1}{\pi}\int_T\lvert f(\tau)\rvert\, d\tau}_{=:Q}\ln\lVert x\rVert 
C:=\max\left\{2,M,Q\right\}
